people cleverer than you

05:40.392 --> 05:42.861
that I'm a feather
in your greasy cap.

05:43.000 --> 05:46.550
I know my writing for you
makes you feel successful.

05:46.583 --> 05:50.463
I know you know
I could walk into any job

05:50.500 --> 05:53.253
and spark grateful tears

05:53.292 --> 05:55.636
from the illiterate
pricks in charge.

05:55.667 --> 05:58.716
I also know you took culture

05:58.750 --> 06:00.798
because you couldn't
get the news desk.

06:00.833 --> 06:04.508
You would censure me?

06:04.542 --> 06:05.984
You're the one
bringing down the tone

06:06.008 --> 06:08.257
with your mealy-mouthed mummery

06:08.292 --> 06:11.876
and your prostration before
the gods of public approval.

06:11.917 --> 06:15.217
I bet you never had a wank
that wasn't focus-grouped,

06:15.250 --> 06:19.460
you sexually craven
provincial nerd.

06:19.500 --> 06:22.834
Why don't you take your
freckled ass on a sabbatical

06:23.083 --> 06:27.338
and let a real man
edit the paper?

06:27.375 --> 06:29.401
