06:38.667 --> 06:42.501
as I do a fucking fountain pen.

06:44.167 --> 06:45.885
Is that all?

06:46.125 --> 06:48.219
No.

06:48.250 --> 06:50.298
Get out. You're fired.

06:54.875 --> 06:56.843
Fine.

07:00.417 --> 07:05.844
'No use denying the fact
we all feel undervalued.

07:06.083 --> 07:08.586
'To be told officially
that we are off the case

07:08.625 --> 07:11.253
'confirms our sense of being
not fully appreciated

07:11.292 --> 07:14.717
'by an insensitive world.

07:14.750 --> 07:17.128
'Paradoxically,
this increases our self-esteem

07:17.167 --> 07:20.592
'because it proves that
we were right all along,

07:20.625 --> 07:23.834
'even when what
we're proved right about

07:23.875 --> 07:27.334
'is that everyone considers us
a waste of skin.

07:29.375 --> 07:31.127
'Finding myself at leisure,

07:31.167 --> 07:33.511
'perhaps I shall have some time

07:33.542 --> 07:35.510
'to craft the burning gems
of literature

07:35.542 --> 07:39.297
'that I was once famous for.

07:39.333 --> 07:41.381
'It was unlikely
a poem would come

07:41.417 --> 07:43.340
'in such peaceful circumstances,

07:43.375 --> 07:44.877
'but you won't get
if you don't ask.

07:45.125 --> 07:48.379
'So, I listed, as is my custom,

07:48.417 --> 07:51.717
'such few words
as my mood suggested.

07:52.000 --> 07:53.877
'Egregious.

07:54.125 --> 07:56.878
'Salsify.

07:56.917 --> 07:58.840
'Monstration.

08:00.583 --> 08:03.211
'The rare words
annoy the punter,

08:03.250 --> 08:06.550
'but they never think
about a poet's lot.

08:06.583 --> 08:10.713
'A painter has oils,
acrylics and pastels.

08:10.750 --> 08:13.720
'Turpentine, linseed,
canvas, sable and hog's hair.

08:14.000 --> 08:16.628
'A musician has entire machines

08:16.667 --> 08:19.876
'of wood, brass,
gut and carbon fiber.

08:20.125 --> 08:22.753
'The poet, though...
Oh, yes, the poor poet.

08:23.000 --> 08:25.674
'Pity the poor bloody poet.'

08:30.208 --> 08:33.256
Roddy?

08:33.292 --> 08:35.760
