09:04.375 --> 09:08.175
Jane Swann. One
of the Berkshire Swanns?

09:08.208 --> 09:14.295
Cast your mind back to a small
font, a baby and a rising poet.

09:19.625 --> 09:21.627
I'm Jane Burrell,
Rebecca's daughter.

09:21.667 --> 09:24.045
Fuck my best boots!

09:27.167 --> 09:29.340
I haven't seen you since
your mother threw me out.

09:29.375 --> 09:31.719
I know.

09:31.750 --> 09:33.798
And I was always
very proud of you.

09:34.042 --> 09:35.701
Two of your poems
were set text at school.

09:35.725 --> 09:37.218
Oh, you should have written.

09:37.250 --> 09:39.423
I would have come and
gabbled at the sixth form.

09:39.458 --> 09:41.711
Well, I hoped I'd find you here.

09:41.750 --> 09:44.754
Where the last of
the semi-famous get assholed.

09:45.000 --> 09:47.844
More than semi-famous.

09:48.083 --> 09:50.506
My friends adore your reviews.

09:50.542 --> 09:52.544
That train has just
pulled out, I'm afraid.

09:52.583 --> 09:54.551
Really?

09:54.583 --> 09:57.883
Sooth. You see before you
a recently fired man.

09:59.500 --> 10:02.128
That is simply the best news.

10:02.167 --> 10:03.339
Is it?

10:03.375 --> 10:05.548
Will you come home with me?

10:07.708 --> 10:09.631
With pleasure.

10:12.750 --> 10:16.709
'Jane's home lived up
to my ripest expectations.

10:16.750 --> 10:19.503
