10:47.333 --> 10:50.667
'In the taxi over, Jane had
mentioned she had a job for me.

10:50.708 --> 10:52.506
'I demurred, of course,

10:52.542 --> 10:54.840
'and asked to be let out
somewhere in St. John's Wood.

10:54.875 --> 10:56.798
